Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:50.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}Then Mr. Yamaguchi and Mr. Honey\Nmet at a coffeehouse by accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:51.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! What the hell am I thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:58.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:01.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Daydreaming about my own\N popularity before I've even debuted!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:05.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What do you wanna do, make people laugh\Nor become a snobby intellectual?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:09.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I want to form a duo\Nwith this Honey Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is express\Nthat feeling to him honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's no need to try and act cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:16.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right! Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:20.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, really, Pootan is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:23.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I even bought the plush figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.41,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\shad0\fnDupree\b0\c&H331A03&\bord0\blur0.5\pos(351.203,65)}Heartwarming Hilarious Comedy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.41,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\c&H68D5EF&\fnNeon\fs52\be2\bord1\pos(351.203,172)}Pootan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.41,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs34\fnDupree\b0\shad0\bord0\c&H331A03&\blur0.5\pos(483.753,405)}Episode 782
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:34.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Pootan, Pootan! Listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:44.68,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\bord0.8\shad2.5}Pootan working hard on pottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What is it, poo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,When I was walking in town earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:40.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,an older man who I've never seen before talked to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:43.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He said "Hey, long time no see!" or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:44.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see. And?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:50.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And he said "Let's go out for a drink\Nonce in a while" and walked off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And what did you do, poo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:57.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what to do, so I said\N"Yes, of course!" or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,because it'd be rude if he were\Nan acquaintance, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:03.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But no matter how much I think about it,\NI think he was confusing me with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:04.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Pootan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:11.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, that has nothing to do with Pootan, poo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:14.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Geez, you're always cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:20.29,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\c&HABF1ED&\fnNeon\fs11\blur0.2\bord0\frz348\frx358\fry316\pos(449.766,110)}Pootan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:20.29,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an3\shad0\c&H8A6C95&\fnNeon\fs10\blur0.4\bord0\frz348\pos(491.684,132)\frx358\fry316}To be\N continued
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:18.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The show will continue on and on, poo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:25.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I watched the show again\N and I think that it really isn't funny at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:30.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But just saying "it's stupid"\N is something that an amateur would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:32.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In any case, as someone who aims\N to be a professional comedian,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I have to analyze why it's so popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:40.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've purchased a book like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:38.19,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\blur0.5\fnGilles' Comic Font\shad0\an1\frz9\bord0\c&H2744AE&\b1\move(181.266,-115,181.266,108,0,920)}It's{\c&H206690&\b0} not too late\N\N\N{\alphaff}a              {\alpha00\frz11} for you to follow it{\c&H2744AE&\i1\b1}!!
