Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and Pootan goods like these...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:48.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,At any rate, it's such a monstrous show that\Nmakes that genius, Honey Boy, go ooh and aah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:50.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's got to be something to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I won't miss any secrets to its popularity,\Neven by a millimeter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:53.37,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\shad0\fnDupree\b0\c&HAF7E3C&\bord0\blur0.5\t(\fs23)\move(590.247,207,365.93,128,0,2948)}Heartwarming Hilarious Comedy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.45,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\shad0\fnDupree\b0\c&HAF7E3C&\bord0\blur0.5\pos(365.93,128)}Heartwarming Hilarious Comedy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:53.37,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\c&H93E9F6&\3c&H85997D&\fnNeon\fs21\be1\bord1\t(\fs32)\move(585.715,250,354.601,194,0,2948)}Pootan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.45,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\c&H93E9F6&\3c&H85997D&\fnNeon\fs32\be1\bord1\pos(354.601,194)}Pootan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:53.37,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\fnDupree\b0\shad0\bord0\c&HAF7E3C&\blur0.5\t(\fs22)\move(645.759,347,458.829,347,0,2906)}Episode 783
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.45,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fnDupree\b0\shad0\bord0\c&HAF7E3C&\blur0.5\pos(458.829,347)}Episode 783
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:53.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I won't miss any secrets to its popularity,\Neven by a millimeter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:58.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pootan, Pootan! Someone\Ncalled out to me in town again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:08.05,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Pootan grinding sesame with a wooden pestle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:01.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Another older man who you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, this time, it was someone I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:04.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So it's okay, right, poo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:08.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But this time I didn't remember his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:11.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see. Something like that\Nhappens often, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It gets very uncomfortable, poo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:15.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was very nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:18.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I managed to cut the conversation short and escaped from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:23.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If it was a buddy of mine or a childhood friend,\NI can get through by calling them "you,"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:27.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but since it was someone from work,\NI couldn't speak that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:31.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was someone from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:34.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,By the way, what do you do, poo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well... I can't tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:42.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But thinking about it, you are a rude person,\Nforgetting your acquaintance's name, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:44.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, that's not really the case, Pootan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why not, poo? Tell me, poo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:50.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Because he didn't remember\Nmy name correctly either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:53.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He called me "Taro" or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:56.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's so funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In any case, what's your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:02.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's not just stupid,\N this show is really confusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:08.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But if I say "it's stupid" carelessly,\N they may say that it's because I'm old-fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:12.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What an unpleasant era this is, that we can't\Nsay "it's stupid" honestly when it's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In a way, it's similar to violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:17.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This isn't good! What am I whining about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:21.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I sound like some dumb comedian\Nwho's envying a popular show.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:24.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Calm down. Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:27.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There must be some secret\Nto the show's popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We've hit rock bottom, Pootan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:34.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see! I got it! The secret\Nof this show's popularity is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:36.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This plush costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:40.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Especially in the realm of comedy, things like\Ncostumes and wigs are universally popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:44.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Strange things tend to captivate\Nthe childlike hearts of people in all eras.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:49.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Innocent children probably\N don't even think there are people in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:53.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's a little makeshift,\N but I'll acknowledge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:57.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In short, it's only these costumes\Nthat are popular, not these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:01.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll now pull myself together\Nand watch the rest of the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:06.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, then, next is the most popular corner\Nof this show, "It's Time for Free Talk."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Is there anything to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:13.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They took them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:20.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I feel that I'm completely used to\Nthe life at Cromartie these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:22.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh? Is that you, Kamiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:24.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:26.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Tabata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I knew it was you, Kamiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:30.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Tabata.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:33.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Since we're going to different high schools,\Nwe haven't seen each other at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:37.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If I remember right, you're going to\NCromartie High School, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:38.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How is Cro-High?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:40.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm doing okay somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Just as I expected from you, Kamiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:47.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I heard that it's tough in Cro-High\Nsince there are many bad kids there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:50.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but I was thinking that you'd be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:56.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I also kinda thought that you\Ncould possibly become like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:09:02.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but while people at Cro-High\Nlook scary, they're actually nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:03.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How about you, Tabata?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:09.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Classes at our Kokaku High are pretty tough,\Nand I'm barely keeping up with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:10.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yoshio is studying hard too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:15.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see. Yoshio has been always\Na hard worker since middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Say hello to Yoshio for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:22.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll tell Yoshio you said hello. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:27.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Tabata is also working hard\Nin a different school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll do my best too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll go home and watch Pootan or something for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:37.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll watch Pootan again and\Nfigure out the reason for its popularity!
