Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:52.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}The coasts in foreign countries\Nare different from ones in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}and you see special beaches and\Nprivate beaches suddenly, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:57.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to just wander around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I stepped on a sea cucumber!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:05.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's all right. It's not poop.\NIt's a sea cucumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:08.79,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs27\fnNeon\b0\shad0\bord0\c&HEDEEF0&\blur0.5\move(11.329,395,-246.975,395,0,1580)}Pootan will not be shown today.
