Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:10.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}I heard that sea cucumbers run away\Nafter throwing up their own internal organs
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}when they come across their enemies.\NThat's scary, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:15.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}Gerotan, the picture and \Nyour lines don't seem to match.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:18.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't worry about it. No nagging, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:22.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It feels good just floating like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:26.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Drifting in the waves... drifting...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Gebebebo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:33.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yay! I easily get seasick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:36.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But it's fun because a lot of fish came to feed, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:42.03,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\an1\fs48\c&H141414&\bord0\frz2\blur0.5\fnBrady Bunch Remastered\b0\pos(188.063,187)}Gerotan\N\N\N{\fnDupree\b1\fs68\frz0}The End
