Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:40.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Gerotan doesn't like parties on\Na houseboat either, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, there's that story too.
