Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:41.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm the main character, Takashi Kamiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's possible that people have forgotten me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(50.981,458)}What's Gerotan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:49.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(50.981,458)}It's a long story,\N so don't ask.
